sub_title: Marie Skłodowska-Curie Research Fellow in Biocatalysis at TU Delft
summary: Interested in all things biocatalysis and currently in the final year of my PhD. My current research includes enzyme characterization, engineering, and immobilization, flow and batch biotransformations, and combining biocatalysis with chemocatalysis. I primarily work with transaminases but also have experience with other classes of enzymes.
